# Only admins may approve changes to scored results, leaderboards, the global
# index, and the generated JSON schemas. Replace @REPLACE-ME-admins with your
# actual GitHub team or user handles before enabling branch protection.
#
# See https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-security/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

tasks/*/results/        @REPLACE-ME-admins
**/leaderboard.json     @REPLACE-ME-admins
/data/                  @REPLACE-ME-admins
/schemas/               @REPLACE-ME-admins
/.github/               @REPLACE-ME-admins
/runner/                @REPLACE-ME-admins
